---

## Experimental Design (BioSense pilot)

**Cohort:** n=30 healthy volunteers (18-65 yr), stratified by age (5 groups × 6).

**Measurements:**
- HRV (24h Holter)
- EEG (30 min resting state)
- Actigraphy (7 days)
- Blood biomarkers: 8 epigenetic/mitochondrial aging markers

**Duration:** 6 months, measurements monthly.

**Power analysis:** Δχ_Ze = 0.2, σ = 0.25, α = 0.05, power = 0.8 → n = 25. Taking n = 30.

**Statistics:** Mixed-effects model (time × age group), Tukey HSD post-hoc. 5-fold cross-validation + hold-out n = 10.

